  <thing id="ra5CBloSus" name="Blood Sustenance" description="You don’t need to eat or drink, except for drinking blood. Using your blood drain to deal at least 1 point of necrotic damage fulfills your daily requirement. \n\nIf you go for 24 hours without drinking blood, your appearance changes, and you become clearly monstrous— gaunt, feral, with prominent fangs and bestial eyes. For each additional 24 hours without blood, you gain a level of exhaustion. When you reach 6 levels of exhaustion, you fall unconscious until fresh blood pours into your mouth." compset="RaceSpec">
