  <thing id="ra5CBiteVa" name="Bite" description="You may bite a creature that is grappled, restrained, or incapacitated. Your bite is a special unarmed strike that deals piercing damage instead of bludgeoning.\n\nWhen you bite a willing victim, you may elect to deal minimum damage, instead of rolling" compset="RaceSpec">
