  <thing id="ra5CBloDra" name="Blood Drain" description="If you bite a living creature with a circulatory system, you drink its blood, and heal an amount equal to 1/2 the necrotic damage dealt. For 24 hours, the victim’s maximum hit points are reduced by the amount of necrotic damage it took from the attack. If the creature’s maximum hit points are reduced to 0, it dies." compset="RaceSpec">
