  <thing id="c5CEldExsV" name="Eldritch Exsanguination" description="Starting at 17th level when you hit a creature with eldritch blast and deal necrotic damage, you may drain its blood remotely. You heal hit points equal to 1/2 the necrotic damage dealt, and the creature’s maximum hit points decrease by an amount equal to the necrotic damage for the next 24 hours. This counts as drinking the creature’s blood for effects that rely on it." compset="ClSpecial">
