  <thing id="sp5CBGBlTh" name="Blood Thrall" description="Prerequisite: 15th level\n\nWhen a living humanoid drinks your blood, you can use a reaction to innately cast dominate person on that creature. If the creature drank your blood willingly, it has disadvantage on the initial saving throw. \n\nThe duration of the effect is 24 hours. Maintaining the effect does not require concentration, but you may only have one dominated creature at a time; using this ability on a second creature frees the first from your control. Using this ability costs 40 hit points." compset="Spell">
