  <thing id="sp5CBGChNi" name="Children of the Night" description="Prerequisite: 7th level\n\nAs an action, you can innately cast conjure animals. The animals summoned are fiends rather than fey creatures. An animal that enters sunlight becomes frightened of the sun until it leaves the sunlight. \n\nUsing this ability costs 20 hit points. You can summon twice as many animals for 40 hit points, three times as many for 60 hit points, and four times as many for 80 hit points." compset="Spell">
