  <thing id="sp5CBGFera" name="Feral" description="You become more savage and bestial.\n\n• Your speed increases by 10 feet, and your jumping distance doubles.\n• You have keen scent and keen hearing, giving you advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on scent or hearing.\n• Your fingernails become sharpened claws. Unarmed strikes that use your claws deal 2d4 slashing damage." compset="Spell">
