  <thing id="sp5CBGInfe" name="Inferno" description="Prerequisite: 7th level\nYou learn the produce flame cantrip. As an action, you can innately cast flaming sphere or wall of fire.\n\nThis costs 5 hit points per spell level, to a maximum of 25 hit points for a 5th-level spell." compset="Spell">
